column5: Went up to the bog in hopes of getting a musky.Got my first it hit (smashed)at night on topwater .than got my first crappie this morning.
Congrats. It must have been a hoot catching a musky on a jitterbug.
Ya i casted it for two hours as my friends argued about how it wasnt a good spot and how the trip was going to be a waste of time .This shut them up
That must of been a thrill just to see your jitterbug get hit by this guy  Did you release it after unhooking the lure??  Leechman
maybe that's my problem, i've been fishing out on my buddy's boat for muskies... i'll just hit the pier next time! lol  nice fish! can't wait to get my first top-water muskie!
Very Nice! And on a top water to boot!!! Jitterbug is a great lure!
ya it was released i didnt measure it but i would estimate it at about 3 feet and ya it was awsome that hitting at night on a topwater.
